   ============================================================================
                            PROPRIETARY COMPONENTS ADDENDUM
   ============================================================================

   The following components of VA21 OS are PROPRIETARY and are NOT covered
   by the Apache License 2.0 above. These require separate licensing:

   1. GUARDIAN AI SYSTEM
      - The complete Guardian AI security system
      - Think>Vet>Act methodology and implementation
      - Security analysis algorithms
      - Threat detection patterns
      - Command validation logic
      - Process monitoring systems

   2. SANDBOX TESTING ENVIRONMENT
      - Virus and malware sandbox testing
      - Isolated execution environments
      - Security quarantine protocols
      - 5-day quarantine implementation

   3. ANTI-HALLUCINATION ENGINE
      - Core anti-hallucination algorithms
      - Timestamped ID generation and validation
      - Cross-validation systems
      - Confidence scoring algorithms

   4. TIERED MEMORY SYSTEM
      - Interconnected tier protocols
      - Context-aware memory management
      - Memory tier synchronization

   5. CONTEXT-AWARE EMBEDDING SYSTEM
      - Context-aware timestamp embedding
      - Tiered tag connections
      - Relevant context extraction algorithms

   6. AGENT ZERO SECURITY INTEGRATION
      - Security monitoring of Agent Zero actions
      - Multi-agent secure execution protocols
      - VA21 Guardian AI oversight mechanisms

   For licensing inquiries regarding Proprietary Components, contact:
   Prayaga Vaibhav - narasimhudumeetsworld@gmail.com

